<title>ạ̉wl ạ̉htmạmạty</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- bklạmk ʿṣbt ʿnyạ wrbṭth ʿlạmẗ ʿly̱ ạ̹ydyạ
 ʿlsẖạn mạbqạsẖ ywm m ạlạ̉yạm ʿạysẖ nạsy ḥqwqk fyạ
 ạlqrạr - whnạm whạqwm wạ̉nạ msẖ nạsy ạ̹nk sydy wtạj fwq rạ̉sy
 lyk rwḥy wqlby wlyk ḥby lyk ạ̉jml ḥtẗ fy ạ̹ḥsạsy
 2- htkwn mạlk kl ḥyạty htkwn ạ̉wl ạ̹htmạmty
 ʿnk hạtklm whạrnm wbsyrtk hạbdạ̉ ḥkạyạty
 3- msẖ rạyḥ mn gẖyrk mṭrḥ mn gẖyrk ạ̉ṣlạ msẖ hạfrḥ
 ạ̉nạ hạmsẖy mʿạk whlạqy njạḥ
 mn gẖyr mạạḥsb wạ̉jmʿ wạ̉ṭrḥ
 4- hạḥlm ʿly̱ qdk msẖ qdy wmʿạk hạdkẖl ạ̉y tḥdy
 wạlnạs hạtsẖwf bʿnyhạ ậyạt wạlbḥr hạytsẖq wạ̉ʿdy</lyrics>
